                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18001029-55-defend471 t18001029-55-punish310"></join>
               Whipped one hundred yards in Thames-street, near Hambro' Wharf
            </rs>.</p>

               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
